import React from 'react'
import { Box, CardFooter, Card, CardBody, Grid,Text } from 'grommet'

const Identifier = ({ children, title, subTitle, size, ...rest }) => (
  <Box gap="small" align="center" {...rest}>
    {children}
    <Box>
      <Text size={size} weight="bold">
        {title}
      </Text>
      <Text size={size}>{subTitle}</Text>
    </Box>
  </Box>
);


function adminAccept() {

    use
    return (
       <Box width='100vw' height='100vh' alignContent='center'>
            <Grid gap="medium" rows="small" columns={{ count: 'fit', size: 'small' }}>
        
          <Card background='red' key='yo'>
            <CardBody pad="small">
              <Identifier
                pad="small"
                title='fs'
                subTitle='ff'
                size="small"
                align="start"
              >
                hi
              </Identifier>
            </CardBody>
            <CardFooter pad={{ horizontal: 'medium', vertical: 'small' }}>
              <Text size="xsmall">hell</Text>
            </CardFooter>
          </Card>
      
      </Grid>

     
       </Box>
    )
}

export default adminAccept
